version_description: We update the Lendlease Plus app as often as possible to make it faster and reliable for you. Here are a few improvements you’ll find in the latest update:   - Further stability tweaks to make your shopping experience better. - Improvements to the sign up process. - Ability to link or unlink your Facebook account via More > View/Edit Profile. - Design updates to accommodate a better experience. - Improvements to push notifications.  Your feedback is valuable to us. Have a question? Tap Contact / Feedback in the app or visit Lendleaseplus.com/contact-us.
